e="margin:0pt 0pt 10pt 14.2pt; text-align:justify"><span style="font-family:'Times New Roman'; font-size:11pt; font-style:italic; font-weight:bold">Sir Bob </span><span style="font-family:'Times New Roman'; font-size:11pt; font-style:italic; font-weight:bold">Kerslake</span><span style="font-family:Calibri; font-size:11pt">: Yes, and there is a modest amount of cost for our own time and costs as well.</span></p><p style="margin:0pt; text-align:justify"><span style="font-family:Calibri; font-size:11pt">&#xa0;</span></p><p style="margin:0pt; text-align:justify; text-indent:36pt"><span style="font-family:Calibri; font-size:11pt; font-style:normal; font-weight:bold">Q65 </span><span style="font:7.0pt 'Times New Roman'">&#xa0; </span><span style="font-family:'Times New Roman'; font-size:11pt; font-weight:bold">Simon Danczuk:</span><span style="font-family:Calibri; font-size:11pt"> You did not seek advice from outside.</span></p><p style="margin:0pt 0pt 10pt 14.2pt; text-align:justify"><span style="font-family:'Times New Roman'; font-size:11pt; font-style:italic; font-weight:bold">Sir Bob </span><span style="font-family:'Times New Roman'; font-size:11pt; font-style:italic; font-weight:bold">Kerslake</span><span style="font-family:Calibri; font-size:11pt">: We have sought some advice, yes.</span></p><p style="margin:0pt 0pt 10pt 36pt; text-align:justify"><span style="font-family:'Times New Roman'; font-size:11pt; font-weight:bold">Simon Danczuk:</span><span style="font-family:Calibri; font-size:11pt"> They charged you for that, presumably.</span></p><p style="margin:0pt 0pt 10pt 14.2pt; text-align:justify"><span style="font-family:'Times New Roman'; font-size:11pt; font-style:italic; font-weight:bold">Sir Bob </span><span style="font-family:'Times New Roman'; font-size:11pt; font-style:italic; font-weight:bold">Kerslake</span><span style="font-family:Calibri; font-size:11pt">: I will give you the figures on that in due course.</span></p><p style="margin:0pt; text-align:jus